33 struct HandleMsgReturn
34 {
35  static constexpr int max_failures = 200;
36  HandleMsgReturn() {}
37 
38  static bool getCorrectMsg(const end_effector_interface::EEButtonStatusConstPtr &data, int value)
39  {
40  bool data_received = false;
41  for (int i = 0; i < max_failures; i++)
42  {
43  if (data && data->action == value)
44  {
45  data_received = true;
46  break;
47  }
48  else
49  {
50  ros::spinOnce();
51  ros::WallDuration(0.01).sleep();
52  }
53  }
54  return data_received;
55  }
56 
57  template <class T> static bool publisherIsOn(const boost::shared_ptr<T const> &data)
58  {
59  bool data_received = false;
60  for (int i = 0; i < max_failures; i++)
61  {
62  if (data)
63  {
64  data_received = true;
65  break;
66  }
67  else
68  {
69  ros::spinOnce();
70  ros::WallDuration(0.01).sleep();
71  }
72  }
73  return data_received;
74  }
75 };
76 // Test service set Digital IO
77 TEST(EndEffectorTestTSuite, serviceTest)
78 {
79  auto client = nh->serviceClient<end_effector_interface::SetEEDigitalOut>("end_effector_interface/set_ee_io_state");
80 
81  // wait for node launched
82  bool exists(client.waitForExistence(ros::Duration(10.0)));
83  EXPECT_TRUE(exists);
84 
85  end_effector_interface::SetEEDigitalOut srv;
86  client.call(srv);
87 
88  EXPECT_EQ(srv.response.state, true);
89 }

91 // check if status of button from driver is published to upper layer or not
92 // in real hw, we can't check because of manually press on button.
93 TEST(EndEffectorTestSuite, publisherTestButtonCustom)
94 {
95  end_effector_interface::EEButtonStatusConstPtr data;
96  ros::Subscriber sub = nh->subscribe<end_effector_interface::EEButtonStatus>("end_effector_interface/custom_button_status", 10,
97  [&data](const end_effector_interface::EEButtonStatusConstPtr msg) { data = msg; });
98 
99  // wait a while to get data from topic
100  bool res = HandleMsgReturn::publisherIsOn<end_effector_interface::EEButtonStatus>(data);
101 
102  ASSERT_EQ(sub.getNumPublishers(), 1U);
103 
104  ASSERT_TRUE(res) << "No data sent from publisher on topic end_effector_interface/custom_button_status";
105 }
